Revision history for Term-Sprog

0.01    05 Dec 2008
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

0.02    11 Dec 2008
        remove the 'use 5.0100' requirement from the module.

0.03    11 Dec 2008
        give correct executable rights to *.pl, *.pm and *.t files.

0.04    11 Dec 2008
        Bug fix in whisper-method.
        add option freq=>'d' which allows a frequency of every 1/10 seconds.
        This requires 'use Time::Hires'.

0.05    06 Apr 2009
        update warranty

0.06    08 Apr 2009
        update licence
